ALTER TYPE [IF EXISTS] <type-name> ...
    ... RENAME [TO | AS] <new-type-name>;
    ... SET COMMENT <description>;
    ... ADD [COLUMN] <name> <column-definition>;
    ... DROP [COLUMN] <name>;
    ... ALTER [COLUMN] <name> <column-definition> ...
         ... [USING <expression>];

Use `HELP COMMAND column-definition` for description of the possible
definitions.
